                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17170501-41-off197 t17170501-41-cd194"></join> last. The Prosecutor deposed, that going to <placeName id="t17170501-41-crimeloc195">a general Court at the East-India-House</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17170501-41-crimeloc195" type="placeName" value="a general Court at the East-India-House"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17170501-41-crimeloc195" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
